# GoNest Roadmap

GoNest is a subscription-based recurring commute platform designed to simplify daily transportation for students, professionals, teachers, and everyday commuters.

Instead of booking rides every day, users create recurring commute plans while drivers receive predictable passengers and more consistent earnings.

---

# 🚀 Vision

Build the world's most trusted recurring commute platform by making daily travel simple, reliable, and efficient.

---

# ✅ Phase 1 — Foundation (Completed)

- Startup idea finalized
- Brand identity created
- GitHub repository established
- Landing page launched
- Waitlist system implemented
- Portfolio integration completed

---

# 🚧 Phase 2 — Minimum Viable Product (MVP)

## User Features

- User registration
- Secure login
- Create recurring commute schedules
- Edit recurring schedules
- Cancel recurring subscriptions
- View upcoming rides
- Ride history

## Driver Features

- Driver registration
- Accept recurring passengers
- Weekly schedule management
- Earnings overview

---

# 📍 Phase 3 — Platform Features

- Smart rider-driver matching
- Google Maps integration
- Live trip tracking
- Notifications and reminders
- Ratings and reviews
- Payment integration
- Subscription management

---

# 📱 Phase 4 — Mobile Experience

- Android application
- iOS application
